column5: Hey guys so here's the story. My dad drives a 18 wheeler and sometimes I go on trips with him. This time we picked up this load of FULLY ELECTRIC ice augers pretty sick  Just thought I'd share this shipment valued at 30 big ones
Let us know the place and time of the proposed "crash site" so we can all scoot over there a grab one from the side of the road.
I know you re a young fella and seeing 500 augers and going on road trips with your old man would be pretty cool. Save us a few woulda ya?
